hasOnlyPublicAncestors

boolean hasOnlyPublicAncestors(String contentId,
                               String slotName,
                               List<String> validFlags)
                               throws com.percussion.services.assembly.PSAssemblyException,
                                      com.percussion.error.PSException
Determines if this item has any non-public ancestors in the given slot name. Will return false if any direct or indirect ancestor item (in the given slot) is in a workflow state that does not have one of the valid flags in it. An item with no parents will return true.

Parameters:
contentId - the content id of the item.
slotName - the name of the slot.
validFlags - the list of valid flags.
Returns:
true if all of the items ancestors in the slot are public.
Throws:
com.percussion.services.assembly.PSAssemblyException
com.percussion.error.PSException
